{{Infobox person | name = David M. Brienza | image = PhotoBrienzaDavid.jpg | birth_date = October 21, 1964 | birth_place = [[New Rochelle]], [[New York (state)|New York]] | alma_mater = [[University of Notre Dame]] [[University of Virginia]] }}
'''David M. Brienza''' is a [[professor]] of [[rehabilitation science]] at [[University of Pittsburgh School of Health and Rehabilitation Sciences]] with additional professorial appointments in bioengineering and electrical engineering.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.stanford.edu/group/resna/Fellows/Brienza.html|title=Hall of Fellows - David M. Brienza|website=web.stanford.edu|access-date=2017-08-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=kpxjQoAAAAAJ&hl=en|title=David Brienza - Google Scholar Citations|website=scholar.google.com|access-date=2017-08-29}}</ref>
He holds a [[Bachelor of Science|B.S.]] from the [[University of Notre Dame]] in [[Electrical Engineering]] (1986) and a [[Master of Science|M.S.]] (1988) and [[Ph.D.]] (1991) in Electrical Engineering from the [[University of Virginia]]. From 1987 to 1991 he worked as a [[research assistant]] at the Rehabilitation Engineering Center at the University of Virginia, and in 1991 he joined the faculty of the [[University of Pittsburgh]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mirm.pitt.edu/our-people/faculty-staff-bios/david-m-brienza-phd/|title=David M. Brienza, PhD {{!}} Regenerative Medicine at the McGowan Institute|website=www.mirm.pitt.edu|language=en-US|access-date=2017-08-29}}</ref> Currently, he is the Director of the Seating and Soft Tissue Biomechanics Laboratory and continues to actively pursue research and development in the areas of [[wheelchair cushion]]s, pressure [[Cutaneous conditions|sore]] and [[bedsore|ulcer]] prevention, [[soft tissue]] [[biomechanics]], [[telerehabilitation]] technology and wheelchair technology.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=289687389&privcapId=7043266&previousCapId=7043266&previousTitle=ROHO,%20Inc.|title=David Brienza: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg|website=www.bloomberg.com|access-date=2017-08-29}}</ref>
